WEBVTT

00:02:58.437 --> 00:03:01.073
ularga kerakli yordamni olish uchun 
hizmat qilgan.

00:03:01.073 --> 00:03:05.335
Qayg'uga jaholat yoki zo'rlovning aksi 
sifatida qaralgan,

00:03:05.335 --> 00:03:09.188
azob chekishni anglatgan va boshqalarni
azoblanayotgan insonga yaqinlashtirgan.

00:03:09.188 --> 00:03:13.545
Bu nafaqat inson, balki jamiyatning ham
gullab-yashnashiga olib kelgan.

00:03:13.545 --> 00:03:16.606
Qayg'u birdamlikni keltirib chiqargan,

00:03:16.606 --> 00:03:20.320
bu esa yashab qolish uchun muhimdir.
Lekin ko'pchilikni o'zimiz bilan bir xil

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:24.067
aziyat chekayotgan insonning 
qayg'usi qiziqtiradi.

00:03:24.067 --> 00:03:25.864
Shoira Emili Dikinson yozgan:

00:03:25.864 --> 00:03:30.396
